snippet.title: The Bornless: Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist The Bornless on Steam and Epic Games Store now:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2411280/The_Bornless/
 
Epic Game Store: https://launcher.store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/the-bornless-6671a5

Sign up at https://www.thebornless.com/ for news, tournaments, and playtesting updates. 

---
 
About The Bornless:

Welcome to The Bornless, an action horror FPS. Face off against other players, summon demons, and build factions in a Lovecraftian world. Use Black Magick, acquire powerful weapons, upgrade your Safehouse,  and strategize to survive. 

---

The Bornless Discord: https://discord.gg/NSDs3UDVCG
The Bornless Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheBornlessGame
The Bornless TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@thebornlessgame
The Bornless Website: https://www.thebornless.com/
Cathedral Studios Website: https://www.cathedral-studios.com/

---
